# MacroMeal Support

Need help with MacroMeal? We can help with account access, subscriptions, meal logging, goals, syncing, and general app issues.

**Support Email:** support@macromeal.app  
**Response Time:** Usually within 1–2 business days.

## Common Support Topics

- Account sign in and password help
- Subscription and billing issues
- Restore purchases
- Food logging issues
- Goals and macro tracking questions
- Syncing and saved data issues
- Bug reports and feature feedback
- Account deletion requests

## Frequently Asked Questions

### How do I reset my password?
Use the sign-in flow in the app and follow the password reset steps associated with your account email.

### How do I restore purchases?
Open the subscription or premium section in the app and use the restore purchases option.

### Why is my subscription not showing up?
Make sure you are signed into the same Apple ID used for the purchase. If it still does not appear, contact support.

### Why are my logs not syncing?
This may be caused by a temporary network issue or delayed refresh. Try reopening the app and checking your connection.

### How do I request account deletion?
Email support@macromeal.app from the email associated with your MacroMeal account and request deletion.

